title: Breathe Carolina - It's Classy, Not Classic [2008]
description:
Description:

Breathe Carolina burst into the scene with their genre creating mix of electronica and screamo. Gaining a huge following in their home town of Denver, word quickly spread via internet about ther amazing live show and self produced demo's. Since then, it's been non-stop. Tours with Jeffree Star and A Skylit Drive and Sky Eats Airplane, BC has the ability to play any type of show whether it's hardcore or a dance party!
